high_descs: Turn right and approach the place on the right.
Take the knife on the table.
Turn left and walk to the small black table on the right.
Slice the vegetable on the top right.
Turn completely around and face the black table again.
Place the knife on the table.
Turn left then turn to face the table again.
Take a slice of vegetable.
Turn right then walk to the microwave.
Place the slice in the microwave, turn it on, then remove it.
Turn around and walk back to the table.
Place the slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight, then turn right towards the left side of the white table.
Take the knife next to the bread on the table.
Go left to the black stand next to the table.
Cut the potato next to the tomato into slices.
Step backwards from the stand.
Put the knife on the black stand to the right of the egg.
Move closer to the black stand.
Take a slice of potato from the stand.
Turn right, go across the room to the oven.
Put the slice of potato in the microwave above the oven. Turn on the microwave. Take the potato from the microwave.
Turn around. Go straight and to the right back to the black stand.
Put the potato on the black stand next to the salt and yellow handle knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato on a stand.

high_descs: Turn right, then another right, walk to the white table
Pick up the silver knife on top of the table
Turn left, walk straight. then turn right to the small black table
Cut the potato on the table into slices with the knife
Turn right, turn left, walk back to the small black table
Put the knife on the small black table
Turn left, then turn right to the small black table
Pick up a slice of potato and turn right
Walk to the black oven, open the microwave on top of the oven, put the potato inside
Close the microwave, set the timer, open the microwave, take out the potato, close the microwave
Turn left, walk straight, turn right to the small black table
Put the potato on top of the small black table
anns.task_desc: Cut and microwave a slice on potato and put in on a table.
